      <div class="prose" style="color:var(--stone);font-size:1.125rem;line-height:1.8;">
        <p>
          Improving your rankings on Google can feel overwhelming, but you don’t need to hire an SEO expert to make meaningful changes.
          With the right approach, you can boost your visibility and attract more traffic to your website and ultimately increase sales
